summary.fRFE Summary function for object of class fRFE
#### Description
A summary function of an object of class fRFE which is the result of the functions selectFunctional,
selectGroup and selectLevel.
#### Usage 
<pre><code>
## S3 method for class 'fRFE'
summary(object, ...)
</code></pre>
#### Arguments
* object An object of class fRFE.
* ... further arguments passed to or from other methods.
